{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894932866,"sessionID":"ses_2846a2e6bffespSqc0M4jSfCzg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b962a34001oVghbcG21njDD7","messageID":"msg_d7b960ad5001WxZ63SkauyxZKi","sessionID":"ses_2846a2e6bffespSqc0M4jSfCzg","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_2ab31831e788478089d902c6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n4: Language: Go\n5: Size: L\n6: \n7: ## 测试任务清单\n8: \n9: ### 1. 核心配置测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go)\n10: - [ ] 测试 `DefaultConfig()` - 验证默认配置值正确\n11: - [ ] 测试 `LoadConfig()` - 环境变量的正确加载\n12:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 有效值\n13:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 无效值（错误处理）\n14:   - [ ] KUBECONFIG 环境变量\n15:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_NAMESPACE 环境变量\n16:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_RESYNC_PERIOD 有效/无效值\n17:   - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_DEBUG 环境变量\n18:   - [ ] 无环境变量时的默认行为\n19: \n20: ### 2. Server 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go)\n21: - [ ] 测试 `NewClient()` \n22:   - [ ] kubeconfig 文件路径提供时\n23:   - [ ] kubeconfig 为空时使用 InClusterConfig\n24:   - [ ] Kubernetes 配置创建失败时的错误处理\n25: - [ ] 测试 `NewServer()`\n26:   - [ ] 成功创建 server 实例\n27:   - [ ] gin 模式设置（debug/release）\n28:   - [ ] 依赖注入正确\n29: - [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n30:   - [ ] 正常启动流程\n31:   - [ ] context 取消时的关闭\n32:   - [ ] HTTP 服务错误处理\n33: - [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n34:   - [ ] 优雅关闭验证\n35: \n36: ### 3. Routes 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/routes_test.go)\n37: - [ ] 测试 `SetupRoutes()` - 路由正确注册\n38: - [ ] 验证所有端点正确绑定\n39: - [ ] 中间件正确应用\n40: \n41: ### 4. Handler 测试\n42: \n43: #### 4.1 AgentRuntime Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime_test.go)\n44: - [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeHandler()`\n45: - [ ] 测试 `CreateAgentRuntime()`\n46:   - [ ] 成功创建 AgentRuntime\n47:   - [ ] 无效 JSON 请求\n48:   - [ ] namespace 缺失\n49:   - [ ] name 缺失\n50:   - [ ] spec.container.image 缺失\n51:   - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误（NotFound, Conflict, Invalid）\n52: - [ ] 测试 `ListAgentRuntimes()`\n53:   - [ ] 成功返回列表\n54:   - [ ] namespace 参数验证\n55:   - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误处理\n56: - [ ] 测试 `GetAgentRuntime()`\n57:   - [ ] 成功获取单个资源\n58:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n59:   - [ ] 参数验证\n60: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateAgentRuntime()`\n61:   - [ ] 成功更新\n62:   - [ ] name 不匹配错误\n63:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n64: - [ ] 测试 `DeleteAgentRuntime()`\n65:   - [ ] 成功删除\n66:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n67: \n68: #### 4.2 CodeInterpreter Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter_test.go)\n69: - [ ] 测试 `NewCodeInterpreterHandler()`\n70: - [ ] 测试 `CreateCodeInterpreter()`\n71:   - [ ] 成功创建\n72:   - [ ] 参数验证（namespace, name, image）\n73:   - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误\n74: - [ ] 测试 `ListCodeInterpreters()`\n75: - [ ] 测试 `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n76: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateCodeInterpreter()`\n77: - [ ] 测试 `DeleteCodeInterpreter()`\n78: \n79: #### 4.3 Sandbox Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go) **[待创建]**\n80: - [ ] 测试 `NewSandboxHandler()`\n81: - [ ] 测试 `HandleAgentRuntimeCreate()`\n82:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n83:   - [ ] 请求体验证\n84:   - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n85:   - [ ] sandbox 创建超时\n86: - [ ] 测试 `HandleCodeInterpreterCreate()`\n87:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n88:   - [ ] CodeInterpreter 不存在\n89:   - [ ] 创建失败回滚\n90: \n91: #### 4.4 Health Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/health_test.go)\n92: - [ ] 测试 `NewHealthHandler()`\n93: - [ ] 测试 `Health()` - 健康检查端点\n94: - [ ] 测试 `SetReady()` - 就绪状态设置\n95: \n96: ### 5. Processor 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor_test.go)\n97: \n98: #### 5.1 辅助函数测试\n99: - [ ] 测试 `RandString()` - 随机字符串生成\n100: - [ ] 测试 `GenerateSessionID()` - session ID 生成格式\n101: \n102: #### 5.2 Getter 函数测试\n103: - [ ] 测试 `GetAgentRuntime()`\n104:   - [ ] 成功获取\n105:   - [ ] lister 为 nil\n106:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n107: - [ ] 测试 `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n108:   - [ ] 成功获取\n109:   - [ ] lister 为 nil\n110:   - [ ] 资源不存在\n111: \n112: #### 5.3 Build 函数测试\n113: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxObject()`\n114:   - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox 对象\n115:   - [ ] 随机后缀生成\n116:   - [ ] 标签和注解正确复制\n117:   - [ ] 容器配置正确转换（command, args, env）\n118:   - [ ] env 的不同类型处理（value, valueFrom）\n119: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxClaimObject()`\n120:   - [ ] 成功构建 claim 对象\n121:   - [ ] 标签正确设置\n122: - [ ] 测试 `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox()`\n123:   - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox\n124:   - [ ] 容器配置正确\n125: \n126: #### 5.4 Pod IP 解析测试\n127: - [ ] 测试 `resolvePodIP()`\n128:   - [ ] pod 直接通过名称找到\n129:   - [ ] pod 未运行状态\n130:   - [ ] pod 无 IP\n131:   - [ ] 通过 label selector 查找\n132:   - [ ] 通过 owner reference 匹配\n133:   - [ ] pod 不存在\n134: \n135: #### 5.5 EntryPoint 构建测试\n136: - [ ] 测试 `BuildEntryPoints()` - 入口点正确构建\n137: \n138: #### 5.6 CreateSandbox 测试\n139: - [ ] 测试 `CreateSandbox()`\n140:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n141:   - [ ] 创建超时回滚\n142:   - [ ] pod 等待超时\n143:   - [ ] warm pool 模式\n144: \n145: #### 5.7 回滚测试\n146: - [ ] 测试 `rollback()` - sandbox 删除回滚\n147: \n148: ### 6. Reconciler 测试\n149: \n150: #### 6.1 Manager 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go) **[待创建]**\n151: - [ ] 测试 `DefaultReconcilerConfig()`\n152: - [ ] 测试 `NewControllerManager()`\n153:   - [ ] 成功创建\n154:   - [ ] 客户端配置（QPS, Burst）\n155:   - [ ] context 初始化\n156: - [ ] 测试 `AddReconciler()`\n157: - [ ] 测试 `SetupEventRecorder()`\n158: - [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n159: - [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n160: - [ ] 测试 getter 方法\n161: - [ ] 测试 `CalculateBackoff()` - 退避算法\n162: - [ ] 测试 `MapObjectReference()` - 对象引用映射\n163: \n164: #### 6.2 AgentRuntime Reconciler 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go) **[待创建]**\n165: - [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeReconciler()`\n166: - [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n167: - [ ] 测试 `processNextWorkItem()`\n168: - [ ] 测试 `Reconcile()`\n169:   - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n170:   - [ ] 删除时间戳设置（资源删除中）\n171:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建成功\n172:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（可重试错误）\n173:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（不可重试错误）\n174:   - [ ] 状态更新成功\n175:   - [ ] 状态更新失败\n176: - [ ] 测试 `getAgentRuntime()`\n177: - [ ] 测试 `reconcileDeletion()`\n178: - [ ] 测试 `reconcileSandboxPod()`\n179:   - [ ] pod 不存在时创建\n180:   - [ ] pod 存在时更新检查\n181: - [ ] 测试 `getSandboxPod()`\n182: - [ ] 测试 enqueue 方法\n183:   - [ ] `EnqueueAgentRuntime()`\n184:   - [ ] `EnqueueUpdate()`\n185:   - [ ] `EnqueueDelete()`\n186:   - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPod()`\n187:   - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPodUpdate()`\n188:   - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPodDelete()`\n189: \n190: #### 6.3 Status Updater 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go) **[待创建]**\n191: - [ ] 测试 `NewStatusUpdater()`\n192: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus()`\n193:   - [ ] 成功更新状态\n194:   - [ ] 更新失败重试\n195: \n196: #### 6.4 Sandbox Processor (Reconciler) 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go) **[待创建]**\n197: - [ ] 测试 `NewSandboxProcessor()`\n198: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxPod()` **[需查看实现]**\n199: - [ ] 测试 `NeedsUpdate()` **[需查看实现]**\n200: - [ ] 测试 `UpdateSandboxPod()` **[需查看实现]**\n201: \n202: #### 6.5 Owner Reference 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference_test.go) **[待创建]**\n203: - [ ] 测试 owner reference 相关函数\n204: \n205: #### 6.6 Error Handling 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors_test.go) **[待创建]**\n206: - [ ] 测试 `IsRetryableError()`\n207: - [ ] 测试错误常量定义\n208: \n209: ### 7. Garbage Collector 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go)\n210: - [ ] 测试 `NewGarbageCollector()`\n211: - [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n212: - [ ] 测试 `Stop()`\n213: - [ ] 测试 `gcLoop()`\n214: - [ ] 测试 `tick()`\n215:   - [ ] 空闲 sandbox 清理\n216:   - [ ] 过期 sandbox 清理\n217:   - [ ] store 错误处理\n218: - [ ] 测试 `deleteSandbox()`\n219:   - [ ] 成功删除 Sandbox\n220:   - [ ] 成功删除 SandboxClaim\n221:   - [ ] 删除失败（ NotFound 错误）\n222:   - [ ] 删除失败（其他错误）\n223:   - [ ] store 删除失败\n224: - [ ] 测试 `recordAudit()`\n225: \n226: ### 8. Middleware 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/request_id_test.go)\n227: - [ ] 测试 `RequestIDMiddleware()`\n228:   - [ ] 请求头已存在 X-Request-ID\n229:   - [ ] 请求头不存在时生成新 UUID\n230:   - [ ] 响应头正确设置\n231:   - [ ] context 中设置 request_id\n232: \n233: ### 9. Response 工具测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go)\n234: - [ ] 测试 `JSON()`\n235: - [ ] 测试 `Created()`\n236: - [ ] 测试 `Error()`\n237: - [ ] 测试 `ErrorWithID()`\n238: \n239: ### 10. Types 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types_test.go) **[待创建]**\n240: - [ ] 测试 `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate()`\n241:   - [ ] kind 为空\n242:   - [ ] kind 不是有效类型\n243:   - [ ] name 为空\n244:   - [ ] namespace 为空\n245:   - [ ] 验证通过\n246: - [ ] 验证常量定义\n247: \n248: ## 待创建测试文件列表\n249: 1. pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go\n250: 2. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go\n251: 3. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go\n252: 4. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go\n253: 5. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go\n254: 6. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference_test.go\n255: 7. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors_test.go\n256: 8. pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types_test.go\n257: \n258: ## 依赖与 Mock\n259: - 需要 Mock 的接口：\n260:   - dynamic.Interface\n261:   - kubernetes.Interface\n262:   - corev1lister.PodLister\n263:   - AgentRuntimeLister\n264:   - CodeInterpreterLister\n265:   - store.Store\n266:   - workqueue.RateLimitingInterface\n267:   - record.EventRecorder\n268: \n269: ## 测试覆盖率目标\n270: - 行覆盖率：≥80%\n271: - 分支覆盖率：≥70%\n272: - 关键路径 100% 覆盖\n\n(End of file - total 272 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\nModule: pkg/workloadmanager\nLanguage: Go\nSize: L\n\n## 测试任务清单\n\n### 1. 核心配置测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `DefaultConfig()` - 验证默认配置值正确\n- [ ] 测试 `LoadConfig()` - 环境变量的正确加载\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 有效值\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 无效值（错误处理）\n  - [ ] KUBECONFIG 环境变量\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_NAMESPACE 环境变量\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_RESYNC_PERIOD 有效/无效值\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_DEBUG 环境变量\n  - [ ] 无环境变量时的默认行为\n\n### 2. Server 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go)","truncated":false,"load