{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895030199,"sessionID":"ses_2846a2e6bffespSqc0M4jSfCzg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b96ceb3001AN15IwVJORKjtH","messageID":"msg_d7b96c1d2001RQmEB24U5PrItZ","sessionID":"ses_2846a2e6bffespSqc0M4jSfCzg","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_6595a94ef04e4a58af4320c1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/docs/docs/architecture/deployment.md","content":"---\nid: deployment\ntitle: Deployment Architecture\nslug: /architecture/deployment\nsidebar_label: Deployment\n---\n\n## Deployment Overview\n\nAgentCube supports flexible deployment models ranging from single-node development environments to multi-cluster production deployments.\n\n## Deployment Modes\n\n### Development Environment (Kind)\n\nFor local development and testing, AgentCube can be deployed on a Kind (Kubernetes in Docker) cluster:\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│         Kind Cluster                │\n│  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  agentcube-system Namespace   │  │\n│  │  - Router Deployment          │  │\n│  │  - Workload Manager           │  │\n│  │  - Redis StatefulSet          │  │\n│  │  - Agentd Deployment          │  │\n│  └───────────────────────────────┘  │\n│  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  default Namespace            │  │\n│  │  - Sandbox Pods               │  │\n│  └───────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Kind Configuration:**\n\n```yaml\nkind: Cluster\napiVersion: kind.x-k8s.io/v1alpha4\nname: agentcube-dev\nnodes:\n- role: control-plane\n  extraPortMappings:\n  - containerPort: 8080\n    hostPort: 8080\n    protocol: TCP\n  - containerPort: 8081\n    hostPort: 8081\n    protocol: TCP\n```\n\n**Resource Requirements (Development):**\n\n| Component | CPU Request | Memory Request | CPU Limit | Memory Limit |\n|-----------|-------------|----------------|-----------|--------------|\n| Router | 50m | 64Mi | 200m | 256Mi |\n| Workload Manager | 100m | 128Mi | 500m | 512Mi |\n| Redis | 100m | 256Mi | 500m | 512Mi |\n| Agentd | 50m | 64Mi | 200m | 256Mi |\n| Sandbox Pod | 50m | 64Mi | 200m | 128Mi |\n\n### Staging Environment (Single Cluster)\n\nFor staging and pre-production testing:\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│         Kubernetes Cluster          │\n│  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  agentcube-system Namespace   │  │\n│  │  - Router (HA, 3 replicas)    │  │\n│  │  - Workload Manager (HA)      │  │\n│  │  - Redis Cluster (3 nodes)    │  │\n│  │  - Agentd (2 replicas)        │  │\n│  └───────────────────────────────┘  │\n│  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  sandboxes Namespace          │  │\n│  │  - Sandbox Pods               │  │\n│  └───────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Resource Requirements (Staging):**\n\n| Component | CPU Request | Memory Request | CPU Limit | Memory Limit |\n|-----------|-------------|----------------|-----------|--------------|\n| Router | 100m | 128Mi | 500m | 512Mi |\n| Workload Manager | 200m | 256Mi | 1000m | 1Gi |\n| Redis (per node) | 500m | 1Gi | 2000m | 4Gi |\n| Agentd | 100m | 128Mi | 500m | 512Mi |\n| Sandbox Pod | 100m | 64Mi | 500m | 128Mi |\n\n### Production Environment (Multi-Cluster)\n\nFor high-availability production deployments:\n\n```\n┌──────────────────┐\n│   Load Balancer  │\n│   (Cloud LB)     │\n└────────┬─────────┘\n         │\n    ┌────┴────┐\n    ▼         ▼\n┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n│Cluster│ │Cluster│\n│  A    │ │  B    │\n│ ┌───┐ │ │ ┌───┐ │\n│ │Rtr│ │ │ │Rtr│ │\n│ └───┘ │ │ └───┘ │\n│ ┌───┐ │ │ ┌───┐ │\n│ │ WM │ │ │ │ WM │ │\n│ └───┘ │ │ └───┘ │\n│ ┌───┐ │ │ ┌───┐ │\n│ │Redis││ │ │Redis││\n│ └───┘ │ │ └───┘ │\n└───────┘ └───────┘\n```\n\n**High Availability Features:**\n\n- **Router**: 3+ replicas with pod disruption budget\n- **Workload Manager**: 2+ replicas with leader election\n- **Redis**: 3-node cluster with sentinel\n- **Agentd**: 2 replicas for redundancy\n- **Multi-zone**: Spread across availability zones\n\n**Resource Requirements (Production per cluster):**\n\n| Component | Replicas | CPU Request | Memory Request | CPU Limit | Memory Limit |\n|-----------|----------|-------------|----------------|-----------|--------------|\n| Router | 3 | 200m | 256Mi | 1000m | 1Gi |\n| Workload Manager | 2 | 500m | 512Mi | 2000m | 2Gi |\n| Redis (per node) | 3 | 1000m | 2Gi | 4000m | 8Gi |\n| Agentd | 2 | 200m | 256Mi | 1000m | 1Gi |\n| Sandbox Pod | - | 100m | 128Mi | 1000m | 512Mi |\n\n## Configuration\n\n### Environment Variables\n\n#### Router\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `ROUTER_PORT` | No | `8080` | HTTP server port |\n| `SESSION_TIMEOUT` | No | `3600s` | Session TTL |\n| `MAX_SESSIONS_PER_CLIENT` | No | `10` | Session limit per client |\n| `STORE_TYPE` | No | `redis` | Store backend (redis/valkey) |\n| `REDIS_ADDR` | Yes* | - | Redis address |\n| `VALKEY_ADDR` | Yes* | - | Valkey address |\n| `JWT_SIGNING_KEY` | Yes | - | JWT secret key |\n\n\\* Required based on `STORE_TYPE`\n\n#### Workload Manager\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `WORKLOAD_PORT` | No | `8081` | HTTP server port |\n| `DEFAULT_NAMESPACE` | No | `default` | Default K8s namespace |\n| `RESOURCE_TIMEOUT` | No | `30s` | Operation timeout |\n| `GC_ENABLED` | No | `true` | Enable garbage collection |\n| `GC_INTERVAL` | No | `60s` | Cleanup interval |\n| `GC_IDLE_TIMEOUT` | No | `300s` | Idle threshold |\n\n#### Agentd\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `AGENTD_PORT` | No | `8082` | Health check port |\n| `CLEANUP_INTERVAL` | No | `60s` | Cleanup cycle interval |\n| `IDLE_TIMEOUT` | No | `300s` | Idle sandbox timeout |\n| `GRACE_PERIOD` | No | `30s` | Termination grace period |\n\n### Helm Values\n\n```yaml\n# values.yaml\nrouter:\n  replicaCount: 3\n  resources:\n    requests:\n      cpu: 200m\n      memory: 256Mi\n    limits:\n      cpu: 1000m\n      memory: 1Gi\n\nworkloadManager:\n  replicaCount: 2\n  resources:\n    requests:\n      cpu: 500m\n      memory: 512Mi\n    limits:\n      cpu: 2000m\n      memory: 2Gi\n\nredis:\n  cluster:\n    enabled: true\n    size: 3\n  resources:\n    requests:\n      cpu: 1000m\n      memory: 2Gi\n    limits:\n      cpu: 4000m\n      memory: 8Gi\n\nagentd:\n  replicaCount: 2\n  resources:\n    requests:\n      cpu: 200m\n      memory: 256Mi\n    limits:\n      cpu: 1000m\n      memory: 1Gi\n```\n\n## Scaling\n\n### Horizontal Scaling\n\n**Router:**\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: autoscaling/v2\nkind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler\nmetadata:\n  name: router-hpa\nspec:\n  scaleTargetRef:\n    apiVersion: apps/v1\n    kind: Deployment\n    name: router\n  minReplicas: 2\n  maxReplicas: 10\n  metrics:\n  - type: Resource\n    resource:\n      name: cpu\n      target:\n        type: Utilization\n        averageUtilization: 70\n```\n\n**Workload Manager:**\n\nThe Workload Manager scales based on sandbox creation queue depth:\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: autoscaling/v2\nkind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler\nmetadata:\n  name: workload-manager-hpa\nspec:\n  scaleTargetRef:\n    apiVersion: apps/v1\n    kind: Deployment\n    name: workload-manager\n  minReplicas: 2\n  maxReplicas: 5\n  metrics:\n  - type: Pods\n    pods:\n      metric:\n        name: sandbox_queue_depth\n      target:\n        type: AverageValue\n        averageValue: 10\n```\n\n### Vertical Scaling\n\nSandbox pods can be configured with different resource profiles:\n\n```yaml\n# Small profile\nresources:\n  requests:\n    cpu: 50m\n    memory: 64Mi\n  limits:\n    cpu: 200m\n    memory: 128Mi\n\n# Medium profile\nresources:\n  requests:\n    cpu: 100m\n    memory: 128Mi\n  limits:\n    cpu: 500m\n    memory: 512Mi\n\n# Large profile\nresources:\n  requests:\n    cpu: 500m\n    memory: 512Mi\n  limits:\n    cpu: 2000m\n    memory: 2Gi\n```\n\n## Storage\n\n### Redis Persistence\n\nFor production deployments, enable Redis persistence:\n\n```yaml\nredis:\n  persistence:\n    enabled: true\n    size: 10Gi\n    storageClass: fast-ssd\n```\n\n### Ephemeral Storage\n\nSandbox pods use ephemeral storage:\n\n```yaml\nephemeralStorage:\n  enabled: true\n  size: 5Gi\n  storageClass: default\n```\n\n## Network\n\n### Service Types\n\n| Component | Service Type | Port |\n|-----------|--------------|------|\n| Router | LoadBalancer | 8080 |\n| Workload Manager | ClusterIP | 8081 |\n| Redis | ClusterIP | 6379 |\n| Agentd | ClusterIP | 8082 |\n\n### Ingress Configuration\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Ingress\nmetadata:\n  name: agentcube-ingress\n  annotations:\n    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/ssl-redirect: \"true\"\nspec:\n  tls:\n  - hosts:\n    - api.agentcube.io\n    secretName: agentcube-tls\n  rules:\n  - host: api.agentcube.io\n    http:\n      paths:\n      - path: /\n        pathType: Prefix\n        backend:\n          service:\n            name: router\n            port:\n              number: 8080\n```\n\n## Monitoring\n\n### Prometheus Integration\n\n```yaml\nmonitoring:\n  enabled: true\n  serviceMonitor:\n    enabled: true\n    scrapeInterval: 30s\n```\n\n### Key Metrics\n\n- `router_requests_total` - Total requests processed\n- `router_session_count` - Active sessions\n- `workload_sandboxes_total` - Total sandboxes\n- `workload_sandboxes_by_phase` - Sandboxes by lifecycle phase\n- `redis_memory_used_bytes` - Redis memory usage\n- `agentd_cleanups_total` - Cleanup cycles completed\n\n## Related Documents\n\n- [Architecture Overview](/architecture/overview)\n- [Security Architecture](/architecture/security)\n- [Deployment Guides](/deployment/kubernetes)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/docs/docs/architecture/deployment.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/docs/docs/architecture/deployment.md","time":{"start":1775895030178,"end":1775895030194}}}}
