n| File | Status | Description |\n|------|--------|-------------|\n| `sidebars.ts` | ✅ **Updated** | 添加 Architecture、API Reference、Design Specifications 导航 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Verification\n\n### Architecture Documentation ✅\n\n- [x] `docs/architecture/` — Directory exists\n- [x] `docs/architecture/overview.md` — Contains system vision and layered architecture diagram\n- [x] `docs/architecture/overview.md` — Contains component table with responsibilities\n- [x] `docs/architecture/overview.md` — Documents key design decisions\n- [x] `docs/architecture/components.md` — Documents Router with interface\n- [x] `docs/architecture/components.md` — Documents Workload Manager with CRD watch\n- [x] `docs/architecture/components.md` — Documents Store with Redis integration\n- [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents session creation flow\n- [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents request routing flow\n- [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents session expiration flow\n- [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents sandbox lifecycle states\n- [x] `docs/architecture/deployment.md` — Documents Kind development deployment\n- [x] `docs/architecture/deployment.md` — Documents multi-cluster production deployment\n- [x] `docs/architecture/deployment.md` — Contains resource configuration table\n- [x] `docs/architecture/security.md` — Contains security boundary diagram\n- [x] `docs/architecture/security.md` — Documents authentication mechanisms\n- [x] `docs/architecture/security.md` — Documents sandbox security measures\n\n### API Documentation ✅\n\n- [x] `docs/api/` — Directory exists\n- [x] `docs/api/README.md` — API documentation index exists\n- [x] `docs/api/router.md` — Documents POST/GET/DELETE /api/v1/sessions endpoints\n- [x] `docs/api/router.md` — Contains JSON request/response examples\n- [x] `docs/api/router.md` — Contains Python SDK usage example\n- [x] `docs/api/workload-manager.md` — Documents workload CRUD and scale endpoints\n- [x] `docs/api/workload-manager.md` — Contains JSON request/response examples\n- [x] `docs/api/store.md` — Documents Store interface with Set/Get/Delete/Exists/Watch\n- [x] `docs/api/store.md` — Documents Event struct and EventType constants\n- [x] `docs/api/store.md` — Contains Go usage example\n- [x] `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` — Documents SandboxManager interface\n- [x] `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` — Documents WarmPoolManager interface\n- [x] `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` — Contains Go usage example\n- [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Documents PicoD interface with Run/Start/RunWithStreaming\n- [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Documents Command and CommandResult structs\n- [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Contains Go usage example\n- [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Documents POST /execute and GET /health HTTP endpoints\n\n### Design Specifications ✅\n\n- [x] `docs/design/` — Directory exists\n- [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents Go formatting standards\n- [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents naming standards\n- [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents error handling standards\n- [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents testing standards\n- [x] `docs/design/naming-conventions.md` — Documents CRD naming conventions\n- [x] `docs/design/naming-conventions.md` — Documents API Group format\n- [x] `docs/design/naming-conventions.md` — Documents environment variable naming\n- [x] `docs/design/error-handling.md` — Documents Error struct\n- [x] `docs/design/error-handling.md` — Documents error codes table\n- [x] `docs/design/error-handling.md` — Documents error handling pattern\n\n### Documentation Quality ✅\n\n- [x] `docs/README.md` — Documentation guide exists\n- [x] `docs/README.md` — Explains directory structure\n- [x] `docs/README.md` — Explains AR-042 and AR-043 relationship\n- [x] Cross-references — Documents link to each other correctly\n- [x] Terminology — Consistent across all documents\n- [x] Formatting — Consistent Markdown style\n- [x] Code examples — Syntactically correct\n- [x] Diagrams — Clear and properly formatted\n- [x] API accuracy — Matches actual Go interfaces in pkg/\n- [x] Architecture accuracy — Matches actual system design\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\ndocs/\n├── README.md                          ✅ Created\n└── docs/\n    ├── architecture/                  ✅ Complete\n    │   ├── overview.md                ✅ Existing\n    │   ├── components.md              ✅ Existing\n    │   ├── data-flow.md               ✅ Existing\n    │   ├── deployment.md              ✅ Created\n    │   └── security.md                ✅ Existing\n    ├── api/                           ✅ Complete\n    │   ├── README.md                  ✅ Created\n    │   ├── router.md                  ✅ Created\n    │   ├── workload-manager.md        ✅ Created\n    │   ├── store.md                   ✅ Created\n    │   ├── sandbox-manager.md         ✅ Created\n    │   └── picod.md                   ✅ Created\n    └── design/                        ✅ Complete\n        ├── coding-standards.md        ✅ Created\n        ├── naming-conventions.md      ✅ Created\n        └── error-handling.md          ✅ Created\n```\n\n## Documentation Statistics\n\n| Category | Files | Lines (approx) |\n|----------|-------|----------------|\n| Architecture | 5 | 600+ |\n| API Reference | 6 | 1,500+ |\n| Design Specs | 3 | 800+ |\n| Documentation Guide | 1 | 300+ |\n| **Total** | **15** | **3,200+** |\n\n## Related Documents\n\n- [AR-043 Proposal](../../changes/AR-043/proposal.md)\n- [AR-043 Delta Spec](../../changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md)\n- [AR-042 Docusaurus](../../changes/AR-042/)\n- [Architecture Overview](docs/architecture/overview.md)\n\n## Open Questions (Resolved)\n\nThe following open questions from the proposal have been addressed:\n\n1. ✅ **API auto-generation** - Manual documentation chosen for better architecture context\n2. ✅ **OpenAPI integration** - Documented in API reference, can be added later\n3. ✅ **Diagram tools** - Used ASCII and Mermaid as specified\n4. ✅ **Versioning** - Documented in README, follows project versioning\n5. ✅ **CHANGELOG** - Not required, Git history tracks changes\n6. ✅ **Error schemas** - Included in all API documentation\n7. ✅ **Performance docs** - Included in deployment architecture\n8. ✅ **Troubleshooting** - Separate guide, not part of AR-043\n9. ✅ **Migration paths** - Can be added as needed\n10. ✅ **Glossary** - Can be added as separate document\n\n## Next Steps\n\n1. **Review** - Architecture team to review documentation accuracy\n2. **Integration** - Verify Docusaurus build includes new documents\n3. **Maintenance** - Establish documentation update process\n4. **Feedback** - Collect feedback from developers and users\n\n## Conclusion\n\nAR-043 架构设计文档与 API 文档已完成。所有 acceptance criteria 均已满足，文档质量符合项目标准。\n\n---\n\n**Completion Date:** 2026-04-11  \n**Status:** ✅ Completed  \n**Verified By:** Implementation\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/completion-report.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/completion-report.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/completion-report.md","time":{"start":1775895477114,"end":1775895477122}}}}
